"" {TEXT -1 62 "It substituted u^3-u^2+2 in place of x to get (u^3-u^2
+2)^2-1." }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 5 "     " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 255 "     This works just like we expect substitution to work
